Gorman reworked with Diana Rikasari x @gormanclothing ♻️

@dianarikasari has created 6 one-off pieces made from past Gorman stock, embodying her vision of reimagining preloved designs to create a new life for garments. Save the date - this limited run will be up for auction on Thursday 28th October at 5:00pm AEDT. All proceeds will be going to @cleanupaustralia, who work to conserve our environment by reducing waste.

